### âœ… Practice:

```python
# Make a list of squares of 1â€“10
squares = [x**2 for x in range(1, 11)]

# Get all letters in a word except vowels
word = "education"
no_vowels = [ch for ch in word if ch not in "aeiou"]

# Multiply only numbers > 3
nums = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
res = [x * 10 for x in nums if x > 3]
